    <p class="mb-3">
      Both the daily and maximum loss limits are set at 6% relative drawdown, meaning the drawdown threshold moves up as your equity increases. This requires consistent risk management, as aggressive position sizing can quickly lead to a breach even on profitable accounts.
    </p>
    <p class="mb-4">
      Instant Funding accounts allow withdrawals from day 1, then every 7 days. Positions must be closed before the weekend — overnight holding is allowed on weekdays only.
    </p>

