      2-Step Classic
    </h3>

    <p class="mb-3">
      The 2-Step Classic follows a traditional two-step structure with a 10% profit target in Phase 1 and 5% in Phase 2. It uses a 4% daily drawdown and 8% maximum drawdown (static), meaning the drawdown threshold does not move up as your equity increases.
    </p>
    <p class="mb-3">
      The static drawdown model provides wider loss limits and more breathing room compared to the relative drawdown on other programmes. A consistency rule applies, limiting how much profit can come from a single day or trade.
    </p>
