      FTP applies a generally flexible rule set, but some restrictions and requirements vary by programme. Review the rules for your specific model before trading.
    </p>

    <div class="space-y-3 mb-6">
      <div class="rounded-lg bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 p-4">
        <p class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-1">Daily Drawdown</p>
