      </div>
      <div class="rounded-lg bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 p-4">
        <p class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-1">Maximum Drawdown</p>
        <p><strong>Instant Funding:</strong> 6% relative. <strong>1-Step Express:</strong> 6% relative. <strong>2-Step Classic:</strong> 8% static.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-lg bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 p-4">
        <p class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-1">News Trading</p>
        <p>News trading is allowed across programmes but you should follow FTP's Risk Review Policy, as excessive volatility exposure may trigger additional scrutiny.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-lg bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 p-4">
        <p class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-1">Expert Advisors (EAs)</p>
        <p>EAs are allowed on <strong>MT5 and cTrader</strong> only. EAs are <strong>not supported</strong> on DXTrade or Match-Trader.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-lg bg-red-50 border border-red-200 p-4">
        <p class="font-bold text-red-900 mb-1">Copy Trading — Prohibited</p>
        <p>Copy trading across accounts is <strong>prohibited</strong>, including copying between FTP accounts or mirroring trades across multiple accounts.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-lg bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 p-4">
        <p class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-1">Weekend &amp; Overnight Holding</p>
