      </div>
      <div class="rounded-lg bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 p-4">
        <p class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-1">Consistency Rule</p>
        <p><strong>2-Step Classic:</strong> A consistency rule applies, limiting how much profit can come from a single day or trade. <strong>Instant Funding and 1-Step Express:</strong> No consistency rule.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-lg bg-amber-50 border border-amber-200 p-4">
        <p class="font-bold text-amber-900 mb-1">Inactivity Rule</p>
        <p>Accounts can be <strong>breached after 30 days</strong> with no trading activity. Make sure to place at least one trade within every 30-day window to keep your account active.</p>
